{"type": "article", "id": 2194, "title": "Paul Smith x Anglepoise 台灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T21:53:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222250RHGnzts9g8x7Phme.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">保罗·史密斯 （ Paul Smith ）联手时尚家居制造商 Anglepoise 联手推出了一款特别版台灯，</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">该款台灯选用了 Anglepoise 最受消费者喜爱的 Type 75 为创作载体，为了使其现代简洁的轮廓看起来更加活力，在其外形上融入了保罗·史密斯最为擅长的色彩元素，浅灰色作为台灯的主色调，灯罩选用了白色，并在支架部分使用了柠檬黄色、浅蓝色和红色作为衬托。定价 200 欧元，</span><a href=\"http://www.paulsmith.co.uk/eu-en/shop/anglepoiser-and-paul-smith-type75tm-table-lamp.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134852ojXb1gl47UFh6fnI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134853efn16hp80IbgKZ3x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261348535nB30CvHOPTxoAq9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}